      "content": "i'll grab the torque wrench and double check the bolts. but man, that noise is so sharp and weirdly rhythmic too. it almost sounds like it's... i don't know, almost intentional? like something is actively making the noise rather than just a part being loose. does that sound crazy or is there any reason a mechanical part would make an \"intentional\" sounding noise?",
